data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET, AT NO FAULT TO SELLERS!!! Welcome to this charming two-story home featuring three spacious bedrooms and two bathrooms. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by an inviting foyer that leads you into the heart of the home. The main level showcases an open-concept floor plan, seamlessly connecting the living room, dining area, and kitchen. The well-equipped kitchen features modern appliances, ample storage space, and an island. ALL APPLIANCES INCLUDED! Adjacent to the kitchen, the dining area provides a cozy space for family meals and entertaining guests. Heading upstairs, you'll find all three bedrooms. Each room is generously sized and designed with comfort in mind. The primary bedroom is a true sanctuary, complete with an en-suite bathroom and a walk-in closet for added convenience. Outside, the property features a well-maintained backyard. Located in a desirable neighborhood, this home offers a convenient lifestyle with easy access to nearby amenities such as schools, parks, shopping centers, and more. With its charming appeal, functional layout, and modern finishes, this two-story, three-bedroom, two-bathroom home is ready to welcome you and your loved ones to a life of comfort and style.
